Description: Use the serial number to find out which explorer comes out with the most treasures and who doesn't survive the adventure. Tags: 5-buttons, 6-buttons, 7-buttons, treasure, explorers
Name: Raiding Temples

Souvenir.Explanation: Souvenir could ask what the starting amount of treasure in the common pool was (requires blanking the module on solve); how much treasure each explorer left the temple with; which explorers died; which round each explorer left the temple; and/or which explorers left the temple first or last.
